### Welcome to Digitaliss' page!
* Greetings. 
* I am Digitaliss. 
* I am a student of computer science at Concordia University and am currently learning my way around Java and Git.
* I am a graduate of McGill University with a Bachelor of Science in Biology.
* Talk to me about biology, programming, League of Legends or board games!
